00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:33,080
It's a bad thing.
是坏事。

81
00:03:33,080 --> 00:03:35,000
So, they get angry, they start yelling at you.
所以，他们会生气，开始对你大喊大叫。

82
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,000
Yeah.
是的。

